(1861, '278', '579', '278/2026/02/1808130226fcgfcf320a.png', 'REF-1861', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 'CANVA PRO PLUS IA 30 DIAS ', '', 'O Canva é a plataforma de design gráfico online mais popular do mundo, perfeita para quem busca criar artes visuais incríveis de forma rápida, intuitiva e profissional. Ideal para empreendedores, marketers, estudantes e designers, o Canva oferece milhares de templates prontos e ferramentas poderosas para você produzir:\r\n\r\n✔ Posts e Stories para Redes Sociais (Instagram, Facebook, Pinterest e mais!)\r\n✔ Apresentações profissionais (PowerPoint, slides criativos)\r\n✔ E-books, infográficos e materiais ricos (alta conversão para negócios)\r\n✔ Logotipos e identidade visual (design de marca fácil)\r\n✔ Materiais impressos (cartões de visita, flyers, convites, banners)\r\n✔ Checklists, planners e templates organizacionais', 37.20, '1', 4.47, 'null', '1', '1', '2026-02-13 18:08:39', '2026-02-13 18:08:39', '1', '2', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', '18', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0.000),
(1860, '277', '578', '277/2026/02/1756130226bfkeb1ifkg.jpeg', 'REF-1860', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 'Xampu Sólido', '', 'Xampu Sólido para couro cabeludo oleoso, caspa, dermatite seborreica, fungos.\\r\\n\\r\\nPor não conter água na composição, se torna um produto concentrado que equivale à aproximadamente 500ml de xampu líquido. Pequeno, fácil de transportar e prático para o dia a dia e viagens.\\r\\n\\r\\nContém surfactantes naturais, emulsificantes, óleos e manteigas vegetais amazônicos, extratos de plantas, argilas, plantas desidratadas em pó, óleos essenciais.\\r\\n\\r\\nPeso aproximado: 70g', 45.00, '2', 45.00, 'null', '1', '1', '2026-02-13 17:56:05', '2026-02-13 17:56:31', '1', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', '10', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0.000),
(1859, '277', '578', '277/2026/02/1731130226b7a6a8ic6c.jpeg', 'REF-1859', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 'Condicionador Multifuncional Sólido', '', 'Pode ser usado como condicionador, como creme de pentear sem enxague e como hidratante corporal.\\r\\nProduto com alta durabilidade, elaborado com emulsificantes, óleos e manteigas vegetais amazônicos, extratos de plantas e óleos essenciais. \\r\\nPeso aproximado: 65g', 45.00, '2', 45.00, 'null', '1', '1', '2026-02-13 17:31:54', '2026-02-13 17:56:19', '1', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', '10', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0.000),
(1858, '277', '578', '277/2026/02/1730130226e8jih29aae.jpeg', 'REF-1858', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 'Xampu Cabelo Seco', '', 'Xampu Sólido emoliente para cabelos secos à normais. Por não conter água na composição, se torna um produto concentrado que equivale à aproximadamente 500ml de xampu líquido. Pequeno, fácil de transportar e prático para o dia a dia e viagens.\r\n\r\nContém surfactantes naturais, emulsificantes, óleos e manteigas vegetais amazônicos, extratos de plantas, argilas, plantas desidratadas em pó, óleos essenciais.\r\nPeso aproximado: 70g', 45.00, '2', 45.00, 'null', '1', '1', '2026-02-13 17:30:30', '2026-02-13 17:30:30', '1', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', '10', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0.000),
(1857, '277', '572', '277/2026/02/1647130226hi4kd4gb0e.jpeg', 'REF-1857', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 'Xarope Expectorante', '', 'Os xaropes fitoterápicos são preparados com plantas medicinais do cerrado, orgânicas e de agricultura familiar, adquiridas da Ervanaria do Marcos Guião.\\r\\n\\r\\nContém: Guaco, Assa Peixe, Angico, Jatobá, Hortelã Vick, Própolis, Gengibre, Açafrão, Melado de Cana.\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\nFrasco com: 120ml', 55.00, '2', 55.00, 'null', '1', '1', '2026-02-13 16:47:00', '2026-02-13 17:13:15', '1', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', '10', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0.000),
(1856, '277', '572', '277/2026/02/1642130226eagdcc606j.jpeg', 'REF-1856', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 'Lubrificante Jambunabis', '', 'Lubrificante Íntimo.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\r\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\r\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nEstimulante íntimo feito com flor de jambú e  plantas estimulantes.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\r\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\r\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nJambunabis - Jambú, extrato de CNB.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\r\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\r\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nFlor Etérea - Jambú, extrato de CNB e psilocibina.', 0.00, '2', 0.00, '[\n    {\n        \"nome\": \"RnJhc2Nv\",\n        \"escolha_minima\": \"MQ==\",\n        \"escolha_maxima\": \"MTA=\",\n        \"item\": [\n            {\n                \"nome\": \"RnJhc2NvIGNvbTogMjBn\",\n                \"descricao\": \"\",\n                \"valor\": \"NjUuMDA=\"\n            },\n            {\n                \"nome\": \"RnJhc2NvIGNvbSAzMGc=\",\n                \"descricao\": \"\",\n                \"valor\": \"ODUuMDA=\"\n            }\n        ]\n    }\n]', '1', '1', '2026-02-13 16:42:43', '2026-02-13 17:12:13', '1', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', '10', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0.000),
(1855, '277', '578', '277/2026/02/16371302262j6h2kaea5.jpeg', 'REF-1855', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 'Tônico Capilar', '', 'Verificar disponibilidade de estoque, caso não tenha, será feito sob encomenda.\\\\\\\\r\\\\\\\\nTemos Tônicos para algumas alopécias, como eflúvio telogeno e alopécia androgenética (cada um com plantas específicas para cada caso) e tônico para condições inflamatórias do couro cabeludo, como dermatite seborreica, caspa, psoríase.\\\\\\\\r\\\\\\\\nFrasco com: 250ml', 75.00, '2', 75.00, 'null', '1', '1', '2026-02-13 16:37:09', '2026-02-13 17:12:47', '1', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', '10', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0.000),
(1854, '277', '572', '277/2026/02/1608130226igbk6c5bih.jpeg', 'REF-1854', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 'Desodorante Natural ', '', 'Livre de alumínio e compostos tóxicos, ele é elaborado com leite de magnésio, óleo de coco, extratos de plantas, própolis e óleos essenciais.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\r\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nFrasco com: 100ml.', 30.00, '2', 30.00, 'null', '1', '1', '2026-02-13 16:08:57', '2026-02-13 17:11:17', '1', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', '10', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0.000),
(1853, '277', '572', '277/2026/02/16071302263fibjfkg0c.jpeg', 'REF-1853', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 'Sabonete Líquido para Área Intima', '', 'Antifúngico, anti-inflamatório. Indicado para auxiliar no tratamento de crises fúngicas.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\r\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nElaborado com barbatimão, aroeira, jurema preta, equinácea, óleos vegetais e óleos essenciais.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\r\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\nFrasco com: 250ml', 75.00, '2', 75.00, '[\n    {\n        \"nome\": \"\",\n        \"escolha_minima\": \"MQ==\",\n        \"escolha_maxima\": \"MQ==\"\n    }\n]', '1', '1', '2026-02-13 16:07:21', '2026-02-13 17:13:05', '1', '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2', '10', NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0.000),
